reviewText: I loved this movie, it had alot of action and C. Thomas Howell is a cutey pie!!! I would recommend this movie! Thank you, Amazon!

Now I am just going to tell you something, all of Thomas Howell's films are definetely all 5 stars, in this film a former race car driver (Howell)who has retired and is the owner of a Mexican Resort Hotel gets mixed up into a robbery involving 2$million by one of his former girlfriends.
